# 【AI-PROMPT】
# 我们在 course_interfaces 里定义 RunMission.action：Goal 含
# mission_file、max_retry_per_waypoint、allow_skip_waypoint；Feedback 带当前 waypoint 和
# elapsed_sec；Result 带 success 和 completed_waypoints。请按 ROS2 action 格式生成字段骨架，注释写清楚各字段含义即可。
#
# 【AI-SCOPE】import · declare · register · 插件/接口空壳
# ========================================================================
# Goal
string mission_file
uint32 max_retry_per_waypoint
bool allow_skip_waypoint
---
# Result
bool success
uint32 completed_waypoints
uint32 failed_waypoints
string final_state
string message
---
# Feedback
uint32 current_waypoint_index
string current_state
float32 distance_remaining
float32 elapsed_sec
